INSERT INTO products (
  id, name, slug, description, regularPrice, salePrice, stock, status,
  categoryId, blessingTemple, blessingMaster, blessingDescription
) VALUES (
  510058,
  'Incense Offering & Consecration Package with Blessed Amulet',
  'incense-offering-consecration-package-blessed-amulet',
  'A comprehensive blessing package combining the sacred rituals of incense offering and consecration (Kāiguāng), with a portable blessed amulet included.

**Incense Offering Ritual:** As the Buddhist scriptures say, "A single petal of incense fills the ten directions, and all Buddhas can smell it." Our monks will perform the incense offering ceremony on your behalf, channeling your sincere wishes to the heavens.

**Consecration (Kāiguāng) Ritual:** This ancient ritual endows objects with spirituality and sacredness through specific ceremonies. In Buddhism, consecration ceremonies are performed by high monks who recite sutras and mantras, awakening the "spiritual essence" of the object and making it a tool to assist believers in their spiritual practice.

**Blessed Amulet Included:** You will receive a consecrated amulet that has been blessed by Wutai Mountain senior monks. These portable talismans can be placed in cars, phone cases, wallets, bedside tables, or carried with you for protection and blessings.

For believers, consecrated items are regarded as a medium connecting them to deities or Buddhist teachings, enhancing faith and dispelling fear. The ritual provides a sense of stability through spiritual connection, helping individuals focus their minds and alleviate anxiety.',
  179.00,
  159.00,
  999,
  'published',
  9,
  'Wutai Mountain Ancient Temple',
  'Wutai Mountain Senior Monks',
  'Traditional incense offering and consecration ceremony performed at Wutai Mountain, Shanxi, China'
);
